  "text": "Sedentary activity was measured by a single question that is part of the IPAQ and has demonstrated acceptable reliability and validity. [CITATION_1] The question asks, \"During the last 7 days, how much time did you usually spend sitting on a weekday?\" Total sedentary activity is expressed in hours of sitting per week.",
